ActBank of Canada Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Finance of DAVID H. LAIDLEY of Montréal, Quebec, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Bank of Canada to hold office during good behaviour for a term ending February 28, 2010, in the place of Jocelyne Pelchat.
